パッケージ ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.distilling

クラス Distiller

java.lang.Object
ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.distilling.Distiller
public class Distiller
extends java.lang.Object
Distills and classifies SourceCodeChange between two Node trees. Changes are attached to the StructureEntityVersion in which the changes happened.
作成者:
Beat Fluri
